Developer Terms of Use
des:
Moments of our childhood is a skill that plays dialogues of several movies so you can have a good time laughing, relax, and remember good times.

You can ask Alexa to save your favorite phrases by saying "Add dialogue to storage".

If you are enjoying this skill we ask you to rate us and leave any comments. You can enter the following link for a satisfaction survey and suggestions to continue improving this skill (https://forms.gle/7YB8B87ysR6GiHkr6).

Enjoy it!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
